        <updateDate>2022-01-21T18:19:15Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Protecting Military Families with Disabilities Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits a landlord who provides housing for Department of Defense installations from collecting a supplemental payment in addition to rent to modify or upgrade a unit to facilitate occupancy by a disabled individual and comply with the Americans with Disabilities Act of 1990.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
